[[File:Emerald detail.png|left|130px]]
An '''emerald''' is a green [[Gems|gem]] used in [[Crafting]] and [[Fletching]]. Emeralds can be cut from [[uncut emerald]]s with level 27 Crafting by using a [[chisel]], granting 67.5 experience. When used with a [[furnace]] and [[jewellery]] [[mould]], they can be used to make emerald jewellery.

One emerald is needed in the [[A Taste of Hope]] [[quest]] in order to turn a [[silver sickle (b)]] into an [[emerald sickle (b)]].

